files.Title: SzeneGenerator.BiomeMapGenerator
files.Summary: Generates biome distribution maps used for terrain texturing and object spawning. Supports simple splits and height/slope-based procedural biome assignment.

files.Title: SzeneGenerator.GlobalSkyManager
files.Summary: Manages global sky, atmosphere, fog, and weather effects such as rain and snow. Follows the camera position and applies region-specific sky presets and weather profiles.

files.Title: SzeneGenerator.HeightMapCreator
files.Summary: Creates procedural heightmaps and control maps for Terrain3D, applying noise, terrain rules, biome blending, and slope-based layer selection.

files.Title: SzeneGenerator.ObjectSpawner
files.Summary: Places environment objects and targets into the scene based on biome, height, slope, and distance rules defined in region configuration. Returns all spawned objects marked as targets.

files.Title: SzeneGenerator.RegionAssetSet
files.Summary: Region-specific asset container used to build a scene. Holds Terrain3D texture slots and prefab mappings referenced by region JSON rules.

files.Title: SzeneGenerator.RegionRules
files.Summary: Region-specific rules loaded from JSON controlling terrain layers, spawning behavior, and local sky settings.

files.Title: SzeneGenerator.SimpleCamera
files.Summary: Free-fly camera with preset views and procedural spawn logic. Can position itself relative to targets while keeping them inside the view frustum.

files.Title: SzeneGenerator.SimpleNoiseGenerator
files.Summary: Lightweight noise-based heightmap generator producing normalized values (0..1).

files.Title: SzeneGenerator.TargetCoordinateExporter
files.Summary: Exports spawned target objects (including metadata like asset_id) to a JSON file.

files.Title: SzeneGenerator.TerrainAssetManager
files.Summary: Creates and applies Terrain3D asset resources (textures) from a RegionAssetSet.

files.Title: SzeneGenerator.TerrainManager
files.Summary: Generates terrain geometry, applies heightmaps and biome texturing, and spawns environment objects based on region configuration. Provides terrain height sampling and target spawn data for camera placement.

files.Title: SzeneGenerator.WorldManager
files.Summary: Central coordinator responsible for building the procedural world. Initializes sky, terrain, spawning, camera placement, and triggers screenshot and metadata export.

files.Title: SzeneGenerator.WorldSettings
files.Summary: Root configuration container for terrain, sky, and camera settings.
